          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This method adds the specified layout guide to the end of the view’s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiview/1622536-layoutguides"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " array. It also assigns the view to the guide’s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uilayoutguide/1619648-owningview"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property. Each guide can have only one owning view."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "After the guide has been added to a view, it can participate in Auto Layout constraints with that view’s hierarchy. "
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
